heading_context: Ask the export support team a question
chunks.html_content: Contact the export support team if you’re a UK business selling goods or services to any market in the world except Ukraine, Russia, Belarus, Israel or the Occupied Palestinian Territories.

heading_context: Ask the export support team a question
chunks.html_content: There are different services for questions about trading with Ukraine, Russia, and Belarus or Israel and the Occupied Palestinian Territories.

heading_context: Ask the export support team a question
chunks.html_content:
You can ask any question for your business, including on:

  • exporting to new markets
  • paperwork you need to sell your goods abroad
  • rules for a specific market where you want to sell services
